Power Armor

Passive
Artificer 1



20% damage reduction vs. physical effects.
10% damage reduction vs. physiological effects.
Your default attack becomes a power-armor punch.
Disabled while you wear armor.
Changes your appearance.

==

==

Might need another effect or two. It's powerful as-is, but is it as powerful as regular armor? It should (eventually) 
be better than high-tier armor.